Generated Narrative: ImplementationGuide ch.fhir.ig.ch-emed-epr

ChEmedEpr

The official URL for this implementation guide is: 

http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-emed-epr/ImplementationGuide/ch.fhir.ig.ch-emed-epr

FHIR Implementation Guide which defines the documents for the exchange of medication information in the context of the Swiss eMedication service

resource.name: Route of Administration
resource.description:
Valueset RouteOfAdministration filtered for ambulatory care use.

This value set is a subset of the mandatory value set ([EDQM - RouteOfAdministration](http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-term/ValueSet/edqm-routeofadministration)) that contains only values compatible with ambulatory care.
We recommend implementers to focus on supporting this value set instead of the complete one.
